How to Detect Meterpreter in Your PC
Antipwny
When you will double click on the software, a dialogue box will open and it will show the meterpreter file running in your computer as shown:right click on the process and select the kill process option.

Antimeter
Antimeter
When you open this software, it will scan the whole computer and it shows the virus containing the file. Also, it will ask you to kill the process or not. So, you type y for yes and the process will die.
